query:
INSERT INTO products (name, slug, description, price, categoryId, materials, colors, images, stockQuantity, isAvailable, isFeatured, createdBy) 
VALUES (
  'Flower Earrings',
  'flower-earrings',
  'Adorable handmade polymer clay flower earrings with yellow centers. Available in pink and blue! Each flower has 5-6 rounded petals and hangs from silver fish-hook ear wires. Perfect for adding a cheerful pop of color to any outfit.',
  7.00,
  (SELECT id FROM categories WHERE slug = 'earrings'),
  '["Polymer clay", "Silver fish-hook ear wires"]',
  '[{"name": "Pink", "hex": "#FFB6D9"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "#87CEEB"}]',
  '[{"color": "Pink", "url": "https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/QhoICKUmUdAJwKyz.png"}, {"color": "Blue", "url": "https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/ELCsvoaXBdLdnoUb.png"}]',
  10,
  true,
  true,
  'both'
);
